慈善機構,就算唔夠10票,都會將總票數合併,多出既仙不論多少一律會作新既一毫計算<br />\n<br />\n善款會喺結算後於歇冬期及賽季結束後各捐出一次,希望大家參與同時,仲可以做埋善事,一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1</a><br />\nclick入上址即可參閱上半季詳盡賽程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/438840/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/438840/page/1</a><br />\nLIHKG香港女神總會盃第二圈抽籤結果<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/390687\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/390687</a><br />\nLIHKG環球女神冠軍盃分組賽抽籤結果"},{"pid":"38c8207a020181a18cee49fe3d981161d58385cd","tid":479033,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T16:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d2b1547308d8cfb36b98efbfe3ec61d2f0b0b7","tid":479033,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T16:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb19f189f5288b33cc8d555096fb49877efec0ff","tid":479033,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T16:39:12.000Z","msg":"香港女神總會盃第三輪秩序 每日賽事開始時間均為當天凌晨零時<br />\n<br />\n第三圈比賽日1- 2017.12.13<br />\n(乙)湯洛雯vs王敏奕(乙)<br />\n(超)張曦雯vs朱智賢(乙)<br />\n(甲)陳嘉寶vs文詠珊(冠)<br />\n(超)趙慧珊@SGvs游蕙禎(甲)<br />\n(甲)黃智雯vs沈卓盈(冠)<br />\n(超)苟芸慧vs岑麗香(冠)<br />\n(冠)林泳淘vs林穎彤(非)<br />\n(超)朱千雪vs陳穎欣@SG(超)<br />\n<br />\n第三圈比賽日2- 2017.12.14<br />\n(超)謝安琪vs陳法拉(冠)<br />\n(非)陳靜vs簡淑兒(超)<br />\n(甲)劉穎鏇vs簡幗儀(冠)<br />\n(超)李靜儀@SGvs杜小喬(超)<br />\n(超)倪晨曦vs陳嘉倩(超)<br />\n(超)林嘉欣vs鄧麗欣(冠)<br />\n(超)麥明詩vs馮盈盈(超)<br 